    section
      topic "human_gated_promotion_ledger"
      statement "An approved lesson is promoted into a durable learning ledger only when the benchmark gate is green and a human approves; a repeated failure is then answered from the ledger instead of being re-derived, which is the concrete payoff of auto learning."
